OL,3,CHunt for Walthamstow vandal smashing
OL,4,Cdozens of car windows every week
OL,6,FDozens of car windows have been
OL,7,Fsmashed by a Walthamstow vandal
OL,8,Fleaving glass strewn across the street
OL,9,Fand residents fearing they'll be
OL,10,Ftargeted next.
OL,12,FNight after night vehicles are being
OL,13,Fdamaged in a crime spree that began in
OL,14,FJuly and shows no sign of stopping.
OL,16,FUp to forty cars are being targeted
OL,17,Feach week and the local MP is meeting
OL,18,Fpeople living in the affected roads to
OL,19,Fwork out how to catch the culprit.
