OL,3,CHunt for Walthamstow vandal smashing
OL,4,Cdozens of car windows every week
OL,6,FOne resident said she "just cried"
OL,7,Fwhen she realised her window had been
OL,8,Fsmashed, adding: "It's just so
OL,9,Fannoying, they've gone through my car,
OL,10,Fsmashed it and they actually haven't
OL,11,Ftaken anything. There's actually
OL,12,Fnothing there was nothing of value in
OL,13,Fthe car.
OL,15,F"I'm a teacher. It's just a load of my
OL,16,Fteaching stuff that they've gone
OL,17,Fthrough and from what I've seen
OL,18,Fthey've not taken anything.
