OL,3,CHunt for Walthamstow vandal smashing
OL,4,Cdozens of car windows every week
OL,6,FShe said Walthamstow was "a lovely
OL,7,Ffamily area" and this happening, "it's
OL,8,Fjust so annoying".
OL,10,F"There's broken glass on every part of
OL,11,Fthe street, every part because they're
OL,12,Fjust able to do it and get away with
OL,13,Fit," she added.
OL,15,FLocal councillor Khevyn Limbajee said
OL,16,Fthe safety of residents was a top
OL,17,Fpriority and the council shared
OL,18,Fconcerns about the spate of vandalism.
