OL,3,CHunt for Walthamstow vandal smashing
OL,4,Cdozens of car windows every week
OL,6,FKhevyn Limbajee said: "We all want to
OL,7,Fsee these crimes being thoroughly
OL,8,Finvestigated and the culprits arrested
OL,9,Fand prosecuted as soon as possible. We
OL,10,Fare doing whatever we can to support
OL,11,Fthe Met Police in achieving this.
OL,13,F"Our network of fixed and deployable
OL,14,FCCTV cameras is monitored 24 hours a
OL,15,Fday, 365 days of the year, and there
OL,16,Fis also a livestream direct to the
OL,17,Fpolice borough control room so they
OL,18,Fcan see footage in real time."
