OL,4,Cdozens of car windows every week
OL,6,FA police statement said: "We have
OL,7,Falready done a number of things to
OL,8,Fcrackdown on the crime and identify
OL,9,Fthe perpetrator or perpetrators.
OL,11,F"Local neighbourhood officers have
OL,12,Fchanged their shift pattern to
OL,13,Fincorporate night shifts, involving
OL,14,Fboth covert and overt patrols. We have
OL,15,Falso requested the assistance of
OL,16,Fanother team to help with night
OL,17,Fpatrols.
