OL,6,F"We've held a number of street
OL,7,Fbriefings with local residents and
OL,8,Fpartners in hot spot locations, with
OL,9,Fmore planned in the future.
OL,11,F"We've also carried out door to door
OL,12,Fenquiries in the area to speak to
OL,13,Fconcerned residents and gather
OL,14,Fevidence, such as dash cam and
OL,15,Fdoorbell footage.
