OL,7,Fof the attacks in mid-August when "one
OL,8,For two cars" were being targeted each
OL,9,Fweek, adding: "We have noticed an
OL,10,Fincrease over the last two months with
OL,11,Fa total of about 50 now incidents
OL,12,Freported to us ` with 25 of those
OL,13,Freported in the last month.
